{"data":[{"id":561133343,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5e546031f7dec33b3a9c3c4fdce228ed","url_token":"shi-zhen-bang-81","name":"孙悟空的狼牙棒","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/dcd326bfd89f102111fb6cbeddab0cba_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/dcd326bfd89f102111fb6cbeddab0cba_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5e546031f7dec33b3a9c3c4fdce228ed","user_type":"people","headline":"任索通吃，漫威DC都看，肯德基麦当劳都喜欢","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":796,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561133343","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545919853,"updated_time":1545919853,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":5,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e事已至此，我只希望最后1月1号呈现给我们的剧情能更精彩一些\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e个人倾向于整个事件是一场剧，至于是一场心血来潮的闹剧还是精心策划的悬疑剧就看作者发挥了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e前天就看到这个问题了，一开始以为是一个高中生真的觉得自己证明了哥猜，然后开始膨胀\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e于是我没说话也没有关注这个问题，因为有一些怀疑，真的这么膨胀的高中生是不会憋一周的，但不知道题主想干嘛\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后我今天看到了“老师”这个角色，还特么是匿名。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e整个事件已经超过了我对现实事件荒诞程度的忍耐极限了，所以忽然好奇作者到底策划了什么样的剧情，决定持续关注着看戏\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只希望作者1.1不要装死\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而且个人觉得1.1之前还有剧情，十分期待\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e目前的剧情推测：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1.主角杳无音信\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e★☆☆☆☆，烂尾了都，退票退票\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2.“老师”说主角“不堪网络暴力”，选择自杀，顺便烧了论文\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e★★☆☆☆，其实也算烂尾，但至少升华了主题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3.主角称自己被威胁禁止发布/论文被偷/主角被谋杀\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e★★★☆☆，期待幕后神秘组织的剧情，但是不太好表现\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e4.主角真的拿出了一篇论文，被指出问题，死不承认\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e★★★★☆，至少用心准备了，一篇正经的论文至少能撑得起硬科幻故事，同时后续剧情还有很大发挥空间\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e5.主角真的证明了哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e★★★★★★，多给你一星不怕你骄傲，这是穿越科幻真人秀吗？穿越者可以这么浪的还真不多见\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不管怎么说，这件事只要有人关注，作者就已经赢了。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我也不呼吁大家不要关注这件事了，我承认作者已经赢了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只希望作者不忘初心，把这个故事讲完，不要吸引一波热度就溜了\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"事已至此，我只希望最后1月1号呈现给我们的剧情能更精彩一些 个人倾向于整个事件是一场剧，至于是一场心血来潮的闹剧还是精心策划的悬疑剧就看作者发挥了 前天就看到这个问题了，一开始以为是一个高中生真的觉得自己证明了哥猜，然后开始膨胀 于是我没说话…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshi